data.description: Beautifully renovated city Townhome close the heart of Allentown. As you enter from the new covered porch, you will see a spacious Living Room & Dining Area featuring Hardwood floors, Brick Accent Wall & Built-in floor to ceiling shelving. A striking New Eat-in Kitchen includes newly installed sliding door with privacy blinds, Refrigerator, Range, Microwave, & Dishwasher plus attractive cabinets. Conveniently located off the Kitchen is a charming Half Bath & a backdoor to a well maintained Trex Deck. There are Three Bedrooms & a Full Bath on the 2nd floor and Two Bedrooms on the 3rd floor. Wash room with sink can be found in the Lower level where there is an outside private baker's alley leading to the front or back yards. The Detached Garage has a new Garage Door and Garage Door Opener and freshly coated roof.
